If some spring cleaning were to be done with an attention to detail, this app would be perfect.

content: Great resource!! Had the previous version since the beginning. Happy to donate an extra buck. This is the third time I've had to pay for the app. It's not expensive by any stretch and is a great app, but when I pay for something that a one-time purchase, I don't expect to have to pay for the same thing again two more times.
replyContent: If it is not too late, ask for a refund and contact me via email (indomitablesoft@gmail.com) with this account.
